    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>The last city on Earth</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The world changed in an instant. Opening an item ???????? It was supposed to give humanity endless energy, but instead it brought only war. When nuclear mushrooms bloomed over the cities, you found yourself in the epicenter of the disaster - in the last surviving metropolis, where the fate of the survivors is now being decided.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3242430/extras/a252b0b05578a820c8e53ba85f0803a0.poster.avif?t=1751669945\" width=800 height=196 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3242430/extras/a252b0b05578a820c8e53ba85f0803a0.webm?t=1751669945\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3242430/extras/a252b0b05578a820c8e53ba85f0803a0.mp4?t=1751669945\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Seconds before...</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Collect as many items as you can before the inevitable happens. Each item will have its own important role in survival, and each forgotten one will bring a lot of problems at the most inopportune moment.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3242430/extras/a0779bd747f13eb58f64a428d173735f.poster.avif?t=1751669945\" width=800 height=196 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3242430/extras/a0779bd747f13eb58f64a428d173735f.webm?t=1751669945\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3242430/extras/a0779bd747f13eb58f64a428d173735f.mp4?t=1751669945\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Survival without rules</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >There are no laws here-just whistling bullets and sharp knives. Every can costs blood, every bottle of water costs a fortune. You will search destroyed apartments, make your way through infected areas, and fight those who have decided that you are their next meal. Even the dogs here are not what they used to be - radiation has made them ruthless predators.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3242430/extras/159e8815ca63b60bc25dec4bc9f0ca3e.poster.avif?t=1751669945\" width=800 height=196 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3242430/extras/159e8815ca63b60bc25dec4bc9f0ca3e.webm?t=1751669945\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3242430/extras/159e8815ca63b60bc25dec4bc9f0ca3e.mp4?t=1751669945\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>The city of secrets and betrayals</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >There is a new danger and a new mystery waiting for you around every corner. Why are there strange tapes scattered around the city and who is their owner? Who are the volunteers really, and who is right about the events in the city? And most importantly, how to get out of this hell alive?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3242430/extras/40d989e8cac42db596c9f84bc685afd4.poster.avif?t=1751669945\" width=800 height=196 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3242430/extras/40d989e8cac42db596c9f84bc685afd4.webm?t=1751669945\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3242430/extras/40d989e8cac42db596c9f84bc685afd4.mp4?t=1751669945\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Your choice is your weapon</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Collect equipment and supplies from whatever you find. Trust those who seem friendly - until they turn their backs on you. Plan every step - one wrong choice, and the city will swallow you forever.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3242430/extras/8aed06f1366e8223fbecf5653cdfbf80.poster.avif?t=1751669945\" width=800 height=196 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3242430/extras/8aed06f1366e8223fbecf5653cdfbf80.webm?t=1751669945\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3242430/extras/8aed06f1366e8223fbecf5653cdfbf80.mp4?t=1751669945\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Welcome to Survival City</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Only those who are willing to do anything survive here.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3242430/extras/024402f53f020ce7152264d68093181a.poster.avif?t=1751669945\" width=800 height=196 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3242430/extras/024402f53f020ce7152264d68093181a.webm?t=1751669945\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3242430/extras/024402f53f020ce7152264d68093181a.mp4?t=1751669945\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
